    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically sound example of the iconic S54-powered platform. The 3.2-liter naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing, providing exceptional throttle response and a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain is complemented by a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been proactively addressed, including the essential rear subframe reinforcement and a recent valve clearance shim service. The chassis architecture remains sharp, featuring aluminum control arms and refreshed dampers for precise turn-in and high-speed stability. This vehicle presents in honest, driver-focused condition, showcasing the peak of BMW\u2019s M-division engineering for the enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical integrity and a visceral, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
