    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered for your consideration is a 2018 Midnight Blue Metallic Executive Sedan, a vehicle that has been treated with care and consistent attention. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though it shows minor, honest signs of use such as light peppering on the hood from motorway travel. The 19-inch alloy wheels are wrapped in premium all-season tires with significant tread depth remaining. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of Graphite leather; the bolsters are firm, and the surfaces have been regularly conditioned to prevent cracking. All electronic features, including the panoramic sunroof, dual-zone climate control, and the 12-speaker surround sound system, operate exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection. Recent service highlights include a fresh oil change, new cabin air filters, and a brake fluid flush. The engine pulls smoothly with no hesitations, and the automatic transmission provides crisp, predictable shifts. This car comes with a clean title, two sets of keys, and a detailed log of its service history. It is a dependable, well-sorted example ready for immediate enjoyment.",
